    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to offer this superlative specimen, maintained in showroom condition. This vehicle exhibits an uncompromising level of preservation, featuring a flawless exterior finish complemented by an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Meticulously serviced and presented in peak mechanical form, this remains a premier choice for the most discerning enthusiast seeking an asset of peerless quality.",
      "price": 44900.0,
